    "code": "<span class='highlight keyword'>class</span> Solution<span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>object</span><span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n    <span class='highlight keyword'>def</span> <span class='highlight object'>maxProduct</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>self</span><span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> nums<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n        large <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> small <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> max_val <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> nums<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>0<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span>\n        <span class='highlight keyword'>for</span> i <span class='highlight keyword'>in</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>range</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>1<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>len</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>nums<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n            num <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> nums<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>i<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span>\n            vals <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> <span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>num<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> small <span class='highlight bracket'>*</span> num<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> large <span class='highlight bracket'>*</span> num<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span>\n            small<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> large <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>min</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>vals<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>max</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>vals<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span>\n            max_val <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>max</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>large<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> max_val<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span>\n        <span class='highlight keyword'>return</span> max_val\n        ",
