    "question": "<div><p>Given an array of size <i>n</i>, find the majority element. The majority element is the element that appears <b>more than</b> <code>⌊ n/2 ⌋</code> times.</p>\n\n<p>You may assume that the array is non-empty and the majority element always exist in the array.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Example 1:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><strong>Input:</strong> [3,2,3]\n<strong>Output:</strong> 3</pre>\n\n<p><strong>Example 2:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><strong>Input:</strong> [2,2,1,1,1,2,2]\n<strong>Output:</strong> 2\n</pre>\n</div>",
    "url": "https://leetcode.com/problems/majority-element/",
    "companies": [
      "Amazon",
      "Apple"
    ],
    "code": "<span class='highlight keyword'>class</span> Solution<span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>object</span><span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n    <span class='highlight keyword'>def</span> <span class='highlight object'>majorityElement</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>self</span><span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> nums<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n        count<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> most_freq_elem <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> 0<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> <span class='highlight buildin-type'>None</span>\n        <span class='highlight keyword'>for</span> num <span class='highlight keyword'>in</span> nums<span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n            <span class='highlight keyword'>if</span> most_freq_elem <span class='highlight keyword'>is</span> <span class='highlight buildin-type'>None</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n                count<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> most_freq_elem <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> 1<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> num\n            <span class='highlight keyword'>elif</span> num <span class='highlight bracket'>!</span><span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> most_freq_elem<span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n                count <span class='highlight bracket'>-</span><span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> 1\n                <span class='highlight keyword'>if</span> count <span class='highlight bracket'>==</span> 0<span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n                    count<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> most_freq_elem <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> 1<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> num\n            <span class='highlight keyword'>elif</span> num <span class='highlight bracket'>==</span> most_freq_elem<span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n                count <span class='highlight bracket'>+</span><span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> 1\n        <span class='highlight keyword'>return</span> most_freq_elem",
