    "code": "<span class='highlight keyword'>class</span> NumArray<span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>object</span><span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n\n    <span class='highlight keyword'>def</span> __init__<span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>self</span><span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> nums<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n        <span class='highlight buildin-type'>self</span>.l_sum <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> l_sum <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> nums\n        <span class='highlight keyword'>for</span> i <span class='highlight keyword'>in</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>range</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>1<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>len</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>l_sum<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span> l_sum<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>i<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span> <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> l_sum<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>i <span class='highlight bracket'>-</span> 1<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span> <span class='highlight bracket'>+</span> l_sum<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>i<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span>\n        \n\n    <span class='highlight keyword'>def</span> <span class='highlight object'>sumRange</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>self</span><span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> i<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> j<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n        <span class='highlight keyword'>return</span> <span class='highlight buildin-type'>self</span>.l_sum<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>j<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span> <span class='highlight bracket'>-</span> <span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>self</span>.l_sum<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>i <span class='highlight bracket'>-</span> 1<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span> <span class='highlight keyword'>if</span> i <span class='highlight bracket'>></span> 0 <span class='highlight keyword'>else</span> 0<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span>\n\n\n<span class='highlight comment'># Your NumArray <span class='highlight buildin-type'>object</span> will be instantiated <span class='highlight keyword'>and</span> called <span class='highlight keyword'>as</span> such<span class='highlight bracket'>:</span></span>\n<span class='highlight comment'># obj <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> NumArray<span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>nums<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span></span>\n<span class='highlight comment'># param_1 <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> obj.<span class='highlight object'>sumRange</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>i<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span>j<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span></span>",
