    "code": "<span class='highlight keyword'>class</span> Solution<span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>object</span><span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n    <span class='highlight keyword'>def</span> <span class='highlight object'>reverseStr</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span><span class='highlight buildin-type'>self</span><span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> s<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> k<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n        cnt<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> i<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> s <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> 0<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> 0<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>list</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>s<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span>\n        <span class='highlight keyword'>while</span> i <span class='highlight bracket'><</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>len</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>s<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n            size <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>min</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>k<span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>len</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>s<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span> <span class='highlight bracket'>-</span> i<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span>\n            <span class='highlight keyword'>if</span> cnt <span class='highlight bracket'>%</span> 2 <span class='highlight bracket'>==</span> 0<span class='highlight bracket'>:</span>\n                <span class='highlight keyword'>for</span> j <span class='highlight keyword'>in</span> <span class='highlight buildin-function'>range</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>size <span class='highlight bracket'>/</span> 2<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span><span class='highlight bracket'>:</span> s<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>i <span class='highlight bracket'>+</span> j<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span><span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> s<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>i <span class='highlight bracket'>+</span> size <span class='highlight bracket'>-</span> j <span class='highlight bracket'>-</span> 1<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span> <span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> s<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>i <span class='highlight bracket'>+</span> size <span class='highlight bracket'>-</span> j <span class='highlight bracket'>-</span> 1<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span><span class='highlight bracket'>,</span> s<span class='highlight bracket'>[</span>i <span class='highlight bracket'>+</span> j<span class='highlight bracket'>]</span>\n            i <span class='highlight bracket'>+</span><span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> size\n            cnt <span class='highlight bracket'>+</span><span class='highlight bracket'>=</span> 1\n        <span class='highlight keyword'>return</span> <span class='highlight string'>''</span>.<span class='highlight object'>join</span><span class='highlight bracket'>(</span>s<span class='highlight bracket'>)</span>",
